file.name: cache_config_03.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: PayloadV
  version: 0.0.0
servers:
  - url: "{server}:{port}/payloadV"
    variables:
      server:
        default: http://localhost
      port:
        default: "9090"
paths:
  /cachingBackEnd:
    get:
      operationId: getCachingbackend
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Ok
          headers:
            Cache-Control:
              schema:
                type: string
                default: "must-revalidate,no-cache=\"field03,fields04\",private=\"\
                  field1,filed2\",max-age=5"
            ETag:
              schema:
                type: string
            Last-Modified:
              schema:
                type: string
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
components: {}

Error: notImplemented: path "/cachingBackEnd": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
